snippet.title: Outland Odyssey Optimization: Crafting & Armor Equipping
snippet.description:
From crafting to equipping, this video has it all to prepare you for your adventure in Avoria!
Don’t forget to always stay alert to Zed drops during quests & hunt for ore deposits, you won’t want to run out of materials in front of the blacksmith.
